    "description": [
        "Episode number 1 of Series \"Climate & man\". This program explains the concept of climate and offers explanations for the variation of climatic conditions which occur on earth as well as looking at the the history of the earth's climate since pre-historic times when dinosaurs roamed the earth. The impact of astronomical phenomena such as sun spots is discussed as well as the climatic implications of another Ice-age."
